explanation: [0-0] The video is displayed in three split screens. The top center screen shows two hands reaching for an orange door. The hands have yellow sleeves, the left hand is blue, and the right hand is green. The orange door has glass on both sides, through which you can see the buildings and lights outside. An orange crescent moon hangs on the door. There are two screens below the video. The left screen shows the same content as the top center screen but in a darker color scheme. The right screen synchronously displays the same content, but from a wider angle. The two arms are connected by a roller. Beside the door, there is a toy Trojan horse, a baby carriage, and a vase on a shelf. The whole picture is in grayscale.
